OL,3,C#19m lost to fraud in a year, PSNI
OL,4,Creveal
OL,6,FMore than 5,200 reports of fraud have
OL,7,Fbeen made to the police in Northern
OL,8,FIreland over a 12-month period, with
OL,9,Fthe total reported loss close to #19
OL,10,Fmillion.
OL,12,FThe figures, from Action Fraud, cover
OL,13,Fthe period from November 1 2023 to
OL,14,FOctober 31 2024.
OL,16,FOver the last year, a diverse range of
OL,17,Fscams have resulted in losses ranging
OL,18,Ffrom hundreds of pounds in ticket
OL,19,Fscams to hundreds of thousands of
OL,20,Fpounds in impersonation and investment
OL,21,Fscams.
