OL,4,Creveal
OL,6,FPolice said many of the frauds are
OL,7,Fcommitted at distance, with criminals
OL,8,Fusing phones, social media, emails and
OL,9,Ftext messages.
OL,11,FSome examples include a bank
OL,12,Fimpersonation scam where a person was
OL,13,Fcalled by someone claiming to be from
OL,14,Ftheir bank telling them there had been
OL,15,Fsuspicious activity on their account,
OL,16,Fand asking for money to be moved into
OL,17,Fdifferent accounts to keep it safe.
OL,19,FIn one instance the total amount
OL,20,Finvolved in this fraud was more than
OL,21,F#100,000.
