OL,4,Creveal
OL,6,FAn online romance scam resulted in the
OL,7,Ftransfer of more than #50,000 `
OL,8,Fallegedly to help with a business
OL,9,Fopportunity.
OL,11,FIn another case an individual lost
OL,12,Fhundreds of thousands of pounds in an
OL,13,Finvestment scam where the person
OL,14,Fbelieved they were part of a genuine
OL,15,Fonline business opportunity.
OL,17,FChairwoman of ScamwiseNI Partnership,
OL,18,FPSNI Superintendent Joanne Gibson,
OL,19,Fsaid the crimes can be emotionally
OL,20,Fdistressing, as well as having a
OL,21,Ffinancial impact.
