OL,4,Creveal
OL,6,FShe said: "Scams are presented in so
OL,7,Fmany different ways and, with advances
OL,8,Fin technology, they can appear genuine
OL,9,Fand as if they're legitimate.
OL,11,F"In terms of the investment scams
OL,12,Fwe've seen reported, often these may
OL,13,Fseem like a good way to boost savings,
OL,14,Fhowever, they are often high-risk
OL,15,Finvestments with limited regulation or
OL,16,Fsafeguards.
