OL,3,C#19m lost to fraud in a year, PSNI
OL,4,Creveal
OL,6,F"While a variety of approaches are
OL,7,Fused, some of them extremely
OL,8,Fsophisticated, the end goal for
OL,9,Fcriminals never changes and that's to
OL,10,Faccess personal and financial details
OL,11,Fwhich are used to commit a more
OL,12,Fsophisticated scam where the losses
OL,13,Fcan be substantial as we've seen from
OL,14,Fthe total losses reported in the last
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,F"It's sickening because people who
OL,18,Fhave placed their trust in someone, or
OL,19,Fbelieved an opportunity to be genuine,
OL,20,Fdiscover in the most cruel way a
OL,21,Fcriminal has stolen their money."
