OL,3,C#19m lost to fraud in a year, PSNI
OL,4,Creveal
OL,6,FThe senior officer urged people to be
OL,7,Fvigilant when anyone makes contact.
OL,9,FShe said: "No one is immune to fraud,
OL,10,Fwe know anyone can be impacted.
OL,12,F"The police service, along with
OL,13,Fpartners in our ScamwiseNI
OL,14,FPartnership, encourage everyone to
OL,15,Fhave a conversation about scams to
OL,16,Fraise awareness.
OL,18,F"This way we can empower each other
OL,19,Fwith the knowledge of how to spot
OL,20,Fscams and stop them, and adopt
OL,21,Fmeasures to protect our information.
OL,26,@qD@KOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
