OL,4,Creveal
OL,6,F"This can include something as simple
OL,7,Fas having different passwords for
OL,8,Fdifferent accounts, and never giving
OL,9,Fout your personal and financial
OL,10,Finformation over the phone to someone
OL,11,Fclaiming to represent your bank. Being
OL,12,Faware can stop the scammer.
OL,14,F"Importantly, if you have lost money
OL,15,Fin a scam please report it ` to
OL,16,Fpolice, your bank and Action Fraud as
OL,17,Fsoon as possible.
OL,19,F"This is key to stopping the
OL,20,Ffraudster's ability to steal more of
OL,21,Fyour money."
